{
  "texts": [
    "Deep learning-based reconstruction methods enable detailed spatial and spectral analysis through readily available RGB images.",
    "With rapid advancements in deep learning, hyperspectral reconstruction techniques are becoming more mature and efficient.",
    "This review highlights the transformative potential of these techniques in revolutionizing agricultural practices, food quality assessment, and postharvest evaluation.",
    "Although the application of reconstruction technologies in agriculture is still in its early stages, as these technologies advance, they are expected to support more sophisticated, accurate, and comprehensive applications.",
    "This progress will transform agriculture and food engineering, opening new research opportunities and enhancing operational efficiency."
  ]
}